For this Error:
.\venv\Scripts\activate : File D:\My 
Work-Usecase\bank_management_system\user_service\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1 cannot be loaded because running     
scripts is disabled on this system. For more information, see about_Execution_Policies at 
https:/go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=135170.
At line:1 char:1
+ .\venv\Scripts\activate
+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    + CategoryInfo          : SecurityError: (:) [], PSSecurityException
    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : UnauthorizedAccess

Solution is this : 
1. Open Windows Powershell
2. Execute this command: Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -scope CurrentUser
3. Press Y
4. if you want you can change it back to restricted mode by executing this command : Set-ExecutionPolicy Restricted -scope CurrentUser
